  Bump

*rivendell-2.0.0_rc0 (21 Feb 2011)

  21 Feb 2011; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net> +rivendell-2.0.0_rc0.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  bumped the beta to a release canidate
  added USE flags to metadata

*rivendell-2.0.0_beta1 (12 Oct 2010)

  12 Oct 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net>
  +rivendell-2.0.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Bumped the beta, dropped 1.7.2 until it builds again.

*rivendell-2.0.0_beta0 (28 Aug 2010)

  28 Aug 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net>
  +rivendell-2.0.0_beta0.ebuild, +files/sandbox.patch:
  The rivendell user and group now has uid and guid set to 150. Jack use
  flag doesn't work right now.

*rivendell-1.7.2 (05 Jun 2010)

  05 Jun 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net> +rivendell-1.7.2.ebuild:
  bump

  12 May 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net> +rivendell-1.7.1.ebuild:
  bump...

*rivendell-1.7.0-r1 (25 Apr 2010)

  25 Apr 2010; Emery Hemingway <emery@icmlf.net +rivendell-1.7.0-r1.ebuild:
  Set rivendell user and group UID to 585 to reduce permissions errors in
  networked systems. Changed /var/snd intial permissions. Moved rivendell
  CGI stuff to /usr/libexec/rd-bin.

